
Use prompt like this during demo:

```md
Use the UI Component Builder agent.

Create a React component from this Figma section:

[Figma link here]

Requirements:
- Use JavaScript, not TypeScript
- Use Tailwind CSS
- First check whether Tailwind is already configured
- Use the existing project structure and conventions
- Use Figma MCP server to inspect the design
- Match exact colors, spacing, typography, border radius, shadows, and layout
- Make it mobile-first and responsive
- Make all user-facing text multilingual/i18n-ready
- Do not hardcode text if i18n exists
- Do not make assumptions
- Ask questions if anything is missing or unclear
- Provide usage example after creating the component
